msgctxt "an5.16:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Balavagga "
msgstr "2. Powers "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: balaaggasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Punakūṭasutta "
msgstr "16. The Peak, Again "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.16:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, balāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five powers. "

msgctxt "an5.16:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.16:1.3"
msgid "Saddhābalaṃ, vīriyabalaṃ, satibalaṃ, samādhibalaṃ, paññābalaṃ—"
msgstr "The powers of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an5.16:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca balāni. "
msgstr "These are the five powers. "

msgctxt "an5.16:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ balānaṃ etaṃ aggaṃ etaṃ saṅgāhikaṃ etaṃ saṅghātaniyaṃ, yadidaṃ paññābalaṃ. "
msgstr "Of these five powers, the power of wisdom is the chief. It holds and binds everything together. "

msgctxt "an5.16:1.6"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kūṭāgārassa etaṃ aggaṃ etaṃ saṅgāhikaṃ etaṃ saṅghātaniyaṃ, yadidaṃ kūṭaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s like a bungalow. The roof-peak is the chief point, which holds and binds everything together. "

msgctxt "an5.16:1.7"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, imesaṃ pañcannaṃ balānaṃ etaṃ aggaṃ etaṃ saṅgāhikaṃ etaṃ saṅghātaniyaṃ, yadidaṃ paññābalan”ti. "
msgstr "In the same way, of these five powers, the power of wisdom is the chief. It holds and binds everything together.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.16:1.8"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
